               <msContents>
                  <summary change="#add-summary2">
                     4 works by 2 authors on the subject of Persian poetry
                  </summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_44548-item1" n="1">
                     <author key="person_76503034" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/76503034/">
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="standard">Amīr Khusraw Dihlavī, ca. 1253-1325</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_10571">Muntakhab-i Maṭlaʻ al-anwār</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_10571">منتخب مطلع الانوار</title>
                     <note>An abridged version of a masnavi poem.</note>
                     <incipit>خطبه قدس است بملک قديم بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم</incipit>
                     <explicit>بتاريخ نهم شهر ذى قعده سنه 32 جلوس همایون عالمگیری بخط ...محمد مختار</explicit>
                     <note>
                        <foreign xml:lang="ar"/>
                     </note>
                     <textLang mainLang="fa">Persian</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_44548-item2" n="2">
                     <author key="person_76503034" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/76503034/">
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="standard">Amīr Khusraw Dihlavī, ca. 1253-1325</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_10572">Muntakhab-i Khusraw va Shīrīn</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_10572">منتخب خسرو و شيرين</title>
                     <note>An abridged version of a masnavi poem</note>
                     <incipit>خداوندا دلم را چشم بگشای بمعراج یقینم راه بنماي</incipit>
                     <note>
                        <foreign xml:lang="ar"/>
                     </note>
                     <textLang mainLang="fa">Persian</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_44548-item3" n="3">
                     <author key="person_76503034" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/76503034/">
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="standard">Amīr Khusraw Dihlavī, ca. 1253-1325</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_10573">Muntakhab-i Laylá va Majnūn</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_10573">منتخب لیلی و مجنون</title>
                     <note>An abridged version of a masnavi poem, written in a rather confused fashion in the centre of the page and the margin on the same folios as an abridgement of Jami's Subhat al-abrar. Extracts of works by Nizami, 'Umar al-Khayyam and Sa'di in the margins at verious places throughout the entire manuscript</note>
                     <incipit>اى داده بدل خزانه راز عقل از تو شده خزينه پرداز</incipit>
                     <note>
                        <foreign xml:lang="ar"/>
                     </note>
                     <textLang mainLang="fa">Persian</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_44548-item4" n="4">
